{"tid":570551,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人同我一樣, 大家一齊圍下爐","createTime":"2018-02-23T18:19:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-25T18:59:56.000Z","uid":69016,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c9b60faef7310b286637d14de9f1b6fea6050cfe","tid":570551,"uid":69016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T18:19:42.000Z","msg":"社交 生活 家庭 好多唔同因素都逼緊你變得堅強<br />\n身邊好多人都淨係識為自己<br />\n自己有難時 未到絕路都唔會向人求救叫人幫<br />\n情況未去到最壞 負面情緒出哂黎之後會突然樂觀返<br />\n好多時就算自己有諗法都好 都寧願犧牲自己 覺得人地開心重要過自己開心<br />\n<br />\n其實好想搵到個地方比自己軟弱下<br />\n好想有人會攬住我 同我講句：辛苦哂<br />\n好想有人會明白我 明白我諗法 明白我處境<br />\n<br />\n有冇人同我一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f9c93385b538283cb01d2b26d27063adb3eb638","tid":570551,"uid":147721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T18:21:06.000Z","msg":"辛苦晒"},{"pid":"a68ea62270742a22ad2123a8fab90517d727d3fb","tid":570551,"uid":71480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T18:23:43.000Z","msg":"辛苦曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22b15df75c6cec60e1a771986ba791833a8821a2","tid":570551,"uid":27482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T18:24:16.000Z","msg":"講得好中<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同你一樣"},{"pid":"3c1e528017261934d05f8b578b5eb383f5f16a2f","tid":570551,"uid":73581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T18:28:56.000Z","msg":"係人面前要扮堅強扮冇事<br />\n夜晚番到屋企熄埋燈之後先可以做番自己<br />\n<br />\n辛苦晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9f32daeb963808f566e3c5e4c256558fdf91fbe","tid":570551,"uid":109459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T19:38:50.000Z","msg":"咁真正嘅你係點㗎？"},{"pid":"56dfb9e9de926ef87bc857ab9c69d4e50b93890a","tid":570551,"uid":69016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f9c93385b538283cb01d2b26d27063adb3eb638","tid":570551,"uid":147721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco